<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tugas Praktikum Modul 2 - CSS</title>
    <style>
        
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #add8e6;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .deskripsi {
            background-color: #d3d3d3;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px; 
        }

        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px; 
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
        }

        .box {
            border: 2px solid #000000;
            padding: 10px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 10px; /* 4.a */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333333;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .box1 {
            background-color: #ff9999; 
        }

        .box2 {
            background-color: #99ff99; 
        }

        .box3 {
            background-color: #9999ff; 
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 28px; 
            }

            .box {
                height: 120px; 
            }

            .deskripsi {
                padding: 12px; 
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Praktikum CSS</h1>

    <p class="deskripsi">
        Halaman ini dibuat untuk memenuhi Tugas Praktikum Modul 2 Pemrograman Web mengenai Pengenalan CSS. Layout di bawah disusun menggunakan mekanisme CSS Grid Layout yang responsif, dikombinasikan dengan penerapan Box Model yang presisi serta manipulasi warna elemen agar memenuhi estetika desain antarmuka.
    </p>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="box box1">Kotak 1</div>
        <div class="box box2">Kotak 2</div>
        <div class="box box3">Kotak 3</div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
